A family business serving the community for over 50 years. We repair most makes of Refrigerators, Freezers, Stoves, Microwaves, Dishwashers, Washers and Dryers. We also sell parts for Do-It-Yourself repairs.
We now have two locations to serve you better. We service Orangeville, Shelburne, Grand Valley, Mono, Caledon, Erin and surrounding areas.
We have a second lactation that serves  Six Mile Lake, Muskoka, Township of Georgian Bay, Coldwater , Port Severn, Bala,  Mactier and surrounding areas.

If the valuable appliances at your home and business are not performing correctly, contact the pros from Mr. Appliance®.We offer upfront pricing, guaranteed labor and parts, and service on your schedule.
***
Mr. Appliance® is North America's leading home and commercial appliance repair franchise system. Established in 1996, our franchises provide full-service home appliance repair and light commercial appliance repair services. We have more than 150 locations throughout the United States and Canada and are consistently ranked among the top home service franchises by Entrepreneur magazine and other industry experts.
***
Mr. Appliance®, along with 11 other nationally recognized home service brands, form “Neighborly: a community of home service experts. If your home is in need of other services or repairs, click to learn more about our community of home service experts.
